{
  "page": "Moro (Century of Blood)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the khal at the end of the third century, see <a href=\"/index.php/Moro\" title=\"Moro\">Moro</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\"><img alt=\"Dothraki.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/50px-Dothraki.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/75px-Dothraki.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/100px-Dothraki.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> <i>Khal</i></span><br />Moro</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\"><img alt=\"Dothraki.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/50px-Dothraki.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/75px-Dothraki.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/100px-Dothraki.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Khal\" title=\"Khal\">Khal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Mengo\" title=\"Mengo\">Mengo</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\nDaughters</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Moro</b> was a <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khal\" title=\"Khal\">khal</a></i> who lived during the <a href=\"/index.php/Century_of_Blood\" title=\"Century of Blood\">Century of Blood</a>. He was the son of Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Mengo\" title=\"Mengo\">Mengo</a>, who had united all <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> in a single <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasar</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moro_(Century_of_Blood)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Moro led the Dothraki to the gates of <a href=\"/index.php/Sathar\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sathar\">Sathar</a>, the \"Waterfall City\" of the <a href=\"/index.php/Tall_Men\" title=\"Tall Men\">Sarnori</a>. All men were put to the sword and their women and children carried off as slaves to the marts of the hill city of <a href=\"/index.php/Hazdahn_Mo\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hazdahn Mo\">Hazdahn Mo</a>, a colony of the <a href=\"/index.php/Ghiscari_Empire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ghiscari Empire\">Ghiscari Empire</a>. Sathar was burned to the ground, and it is written that Moro gave the ruins a new name: Yalli Qamayi, the place of Wailing Children.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Six years later, Moro razed <a href=\"/index.php/Kasath\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kasath\">Kasath</a> to the ground, with the aid of the King of <a href=\"/index.php/Gornath\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Gornath\">Gornath</a>, who had taken one of Moro's daughters as wife and made common cause with him and sent aid to Moro's riders. Twelve years later, however, Moro was slain by Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Horro\" title=\"Horro\">Horro</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moro_(Century_of_Blood)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Doshi\" title=\"Doshi\">Doshi</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; paddin